Spec: Agent Plugin Source

Purpose:
  Own shared skill templates, product plugin templates, reusable fragments, shared files, and build scripts.

Owns:
  ./skills/**
  ./plugins/**
  ./shared/**
  ./fragments/**
  ./build/**

Must:
  Treat source files as the editable authority for generated `../plugins/*` submodule output.
  Keep shared files centralized under `./shared` or repository-level files when reused by multiple plugin targets.
  Keep generated plugin output deterministic and committed in each plugin submodule.

Must not:
  Store marketplace-only skill behavior outside source templates.
  Duplicate shared assets or licenses in product plugin source templates.
